{
  "stem": "14168.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, at the time it was 1937.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Jews were excluded from any Winter Relief, which was the winter-- German Winter Relief work, which helped the poor people, gave them-- they collected the food and they collected clothes, which was then doled out to the poor people.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It so happened that on one Sunday, nobody was home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They left a ticket that they had been there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- my mother said next Monday, when I cut classes, she said, you better go over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's a Jewish family across the street, and there the collecting station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went there, and I was received by a very lovely lady there, who knew my family and engaged me in a very interesting conversation-- political-- and whom I-- she knew my family.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A little while later, a few minutes later, the door opened, and a lovely young girl came in-- her daughter-- wondering what her mother was doing-- who she was talking to.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was drawn into the conversation, and I was drawn towards her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She looked beautiful, and she seemed to be a very intelligent person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after we got through, I delivered everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, do you belong to the Zionist movement?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, well, I'm not so convinced of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, well, can we continue our discussion sometime later?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she said, well, if you are interested.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we continued our discussion on some other date.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And afterwards, I said, could we also meet privately, socially?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was, obviously, shaken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she-- and she was not too enthused.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But, in my life, I have seldom taken no for an answer, and so I didn't.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She went to the-- she had gone to a public-- to a gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
